                        <h6><a href="#">TERMS &amp; CONDITIONS</a></h6>
                        <p>By submitting a purchase order for White Sun Crafts, you are agreeing to the following:</p>
                        <ul class="terms">
                            <li><strong>Adding to Orders</strong> Once an order is placed, we cannot add items to your order. You will need to submit a new order for the items you forgot.</li>
                            <li><strong>Combining Orders</strong> If you place an additional order, shipping will be combined, but only if the previous order has not yet been packaged. If you're concerned about a shipping refund, please <a href="~/Contact.aspx" runat="server">contact us</a> prior to submitting the additional order.</li>
                            <li><strong>Custom Orders/Special Requests</strong> If you request a special item specifcially for you, you must agree to payment prior to the item being made or ordered.</li>
                            <li><strong>Refunds/Exchanges</strong> If you receive your order and find a damaged or missing item, you must <a href="~/Contact.aspx" runat="server">contact us</a> within 1 week of receiving your order. Any refunds or exchanges are at the discretion of White Sun Crafts.
                                <ul>
                                    <li>If you receive an incorrect item, it must be unopened and re-sellable in order to receive a full refund. Again, you must contact us within 1 week of receiving the incorrect item.</li>
                                    <li>You cannot exchange items based on "changing your mind" about a purchase.</li>
                                    <li>White Sun Crafts does not offer store credit for refunds or exchanges.</li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                            <li><strong>Sales Tax</strong> White Sun Crafts is located in Missouri. Therefore, all Missouri customers are required to pay a sales tax rate of 8.225% (includes shipping).</li>
                            <li><strong>Holding Orders</strong> Orders cannot be held. Unless noted otherwise, all orders placed by 9:00pm CST will be shipped the next day.</li>
                            <li><strong>Lost/Missing Orders</strong> Tracking will be provided on all orders. Once USPS has verified that your package has been shipped, it is out of White Sun Crafts' control. Orders will be replaced at the buyer's expense if the order does not arrive.</li>
                            <li><strong>Terms and Conditions</strong> The above Terms and Conditions are subject to change as necessary at any time. It is your responsibility as the buyer to stay updated on these terms.</li>
